      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING BJORN (1) was well supported last time but could only manage third (25.91), beaten 7 lengths. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Top chance in this line up. ZIPPY TIPPY (3) is a talented type who skirted wide from an outside draw and crossed down to the inside, leading throughout to win (25.42) at this track in Mix over 450m. Superior out of the boxes and will be in the firing line early. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Bold showing expected again. CHARGED (6) stalked the lead from a low draw and fought on well to finish 2.5 lengths back in second (25.70) at this track in a Mix over 450m. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in two starts. Overdue and is among the main hopes. WITCHY WOMAN (2) placed last time (25.52) at this track in a Mix, finishing second and beaten 1.5 lengths. Already a winner from this draw.",
